com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.socket

Class SocketAdapterRawTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.socket.SocketAdapterRawTransformer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFromMessageTransformer, IMessageTransformer, IToMessageTransformer, IMessageProcessorEventTransformer

    public class SocketAdapterRawTransformer
extends Object
implements IMessageTransformer, IMessageProcessorEventTransformer
    This is a raw transformer for messages and events that uses a session identifier in event transformations. It takes a Property partyDelimiter which is used to delimit Our Party and Their Party in the SessionID. The default for this delimiter is "_".

    Internally this adapter delegates to a StandardFixTransformer to perform the from/to IFIXMessage transformation.

    Author:
    Paddy Atherstone
